<section id="gls_ref">
  <title>ref</title>

  <para>Reference - points to a span of source or target text within the same unit, to which the
    glossary entry is relevant.</para>

  <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> IRI</para>

  <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> undefined</para>

  <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
    <olink targetdoc="../elements/glossary/glossentry.xml"
      targetptr="glossentry"><code>&lt;glossEntry></code></olink> and <olink targetdoc="../elements/glossary/translation.xml"
        targetptr="translation"><code>&lt;translation></code></olink>.</para>

  <itemizedlist>
    <title>Constraints</title>

    <listitem>
      <para>The value of the <olink targetdoc="gls_ref.xml" targetptr="gls_ref"
          ><code>ref</code></olink> attribute <glossterm>MUST</glossterm> point to a span of text
        within the same <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"
            ><code>&lt;unit></code></olink> element, where the enclosing <olink
          targetdoc="../elements/glossary/glossary.xml" targetptr="glossary"
            ><code>&lt;glossary></code></olink> element is located.</para>
      
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
</section>
